2023-2024 - Points

Desmond Bane scores a season high 49 points for Memphis Grizzlies

On December 12, 2023, Desmond Bane set a season high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 49 points in Memphis Grizzlies's road win against Detroit Pistons, 102-116. He also had 6 rebounds, 8 assists, 1 steal and finished the game with a 51 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Rebounds

Jordan Goodwin grabs a season high 19 rebounds for Memphis Grizzlies

On April 04, 2024, Jordan Goodwin set a season high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 19 rebounds in Memphis Grizzlies's home loss against San Antonio Spurs, 87-102. He also had 10 points, 5 assists and finished the game with a 23 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Assists

Desmond Bane dishes a season high 16 assists for Memphis Grizzlies

On March 03, 2024, Desmond Bane set a season high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 16 assists in Memphis Grizzlies's home loss against Los Angeles Lakers, 124-136. He also had 26 points, 4 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 34 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Steals

Jaren Jackson Jr. has a season high 6 steals for Memphis Grizzlies

On January 01, 2024, Jaren Jackson Jr. set a season high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 6 steals in Memphis Grizzlies's road win against Toronto Raptors, 100-108. He also had 27 points, 4 rebounds, 6 steals and finished the game with a 27 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Blocks

Jaren Jackson Jr. blocks a season high 6 blocks for Memphis Grizzlies Jaren Jackson Jr.

On November 11, 2023, Jaren Jackson Jr. set a season high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 6 blocks in Memphis Grizzlies's home win against Utah Jazz, 105-91. He also had 20 points, 6 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 22 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Efficiency

Desmond Bane set a season high 51 efficiency for Memphis Grizzlies

On December 12, 2023, Desmond Bane set a season high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 51 efficiency in Memphis Grizzlies's road win against Detroit Pistons, 102-116. He also had 49 points, 6 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 51 efficiency.
